dcterms:description: This dataset contains synthetic graphs generated by the Erdös-Rényi (E-R) model, where each graph consists of two 10-node communities. The label is determined by the average node degree in the first community.
dcterms:title: Community

dcterms:description: In this dataset, each graph represents a molecule, where each node corresponds to an atom and each edge represents a chemical bond. The dataset is used for molecular machine learning tasks.
dcterms:title: Ogbg-molhiv

dcterms:description: This dataset contains movie collaboration networks from IMDB, where each node represents an actor or actress, and each edge represents the collaboration between two actors or actresses in the same movie.
dcterms:title: IMDB-M
